cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with recognizing situations in images. It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it involves predicting the most salient verb and filling its semantic roles. The use of neural networks suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
